Excited to share my company I began working on during my rehab that has become a true passion project for me!

Introducing The Chew Club @chewclub. With 3 amazing sons/pups of my own, I have been searching for a brand I can trust with no mystery ingredients that my pups can enjoy - we now have that! 

The Chew Club is a solution for your dog's chewing needs! The days of your couch, shoes and belts being destroyed are no longer. With our Chew Club toys, chews, treats, and powerbones your pups will have more than enough to chew and stay happy! 

@gerrymarshallandcash, this was all for you! Leave my belts alone. 

In honor of our launch, click the link in my bio use code TYLER25 to get 25% off your first order or subscription box.
